Help:Node.title: Command Usage: !badnames
Help:Node.Log:Description:
COMMAND USAGE: !badnames
EXAMPLE: !badnames
Lists all of the names currently on the bad names list for the game you're logged in to. These are names that may not be used as character names and are typically offensive words or names that have a specific importance to a game.
SEE ALSO: !badname, !goodname
